# Cursor Rules

## Design System
- Always use CSS custom properties from `src/styles/tokens.css`
- Never use raw hex colors - use design tokens instead
- Use semantic color names (e.g., `--color-text-primary` not `--color-blue-500`)

## Accessibility
- All interactive elements must have AA-compliant focus rings
- Use `var(--shadow-focus)` for focus styles
- Maintain color contrast ratios of 4.5:1 minimum

## Code Style
- Use consistent naming: kebab-case for CSS, camelCase for JS
- Prefer CSS custom properties over hardcoded values
- Keep components modular and reusable

## File Organization
- Design tokens in `design/tokens.json`
- CSS variables in `src/styles/tokens.css`
- Global styles in `src/styles/globals.css`
- Component scripts in `src/js/`
- Media assets in `public/media/` and `public/logos/`
